<table border="0" height="600" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="1007" style="background:url(images/bg1.jpg)" align="center">
<!-- fwtable fwsrc="未命名" fwbase="sr.jpg" fwstyle="Dreamweaver" fwdocid = "1344182167" fwnested="1" -->
  <tr><!-- row 1 -->
    <td align="right" valign="top">
    
		<!--标题开始-->
	      <div style="font-family:'华文行楷'; font-size:18pt;  color:#411500; text-align:center; padding-top:15px;">
	      	黃帝《陰符經》講義(續完)（二）
	      </div>
	      <!-- 副标题 -->
	      <div style="font-family:'华文行楷'; font-size:16pt;  color:#411500; text-align:center; padding-top:15px;">
	      	
	      </div>
	      <!--标题结束-->
		<div style="text-align:center"><a name="1" id="1"></a>
		<img name="sr_r3_c1" src="images/sr_r3_c1.gif" width="293" height="32" border="0" id="sr_r3_c1" alt="" /></div>
		<!--图片-->
		
		<!--图片结束-->
		<!-- 作者 -->
		
			<div style="font-family:'宋体'; font-size:12pt;  color:#411500; text-align:center;padding-bottom:8px;">
		      	
		    </div>
		
	   <div style="text-align:left; color:#88510c; font-size:14px; line-height:20px; width:900px; height:auto; margin:0 auto;">
	   		<!-- 显示内容 -->
	   		<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">三、強兵戰勝演術章</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">瞽</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">者</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">善</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">聽，聾者</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">善</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">視，絕利一</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">源</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">，用師十倍，三反</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">晝</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">夜，用師萬倍。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;利<font face="Times New Roman">:</font><font face="宋体">指快利耳</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">目</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">，牽引神心的聲色名利等。源<font face="Times New Roman">:</font><font face="宋体">恨，因</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">由</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;三反<font face="Times New Roman">:</font><font face="宋体">是指眼</font><font face="Times New Roman">(</font><font face="宋体">收視</font><font face="Times New Roman">)</font><font face="宋体">、耳</font><font face="Times New Roman">(</font><font face="宋体">返聽</font><font face="Times New Roman">)</font><font face="宋体">、口</font><font face="Times New Roman">(</font><font face="宋体">希言</font><font face="Times New Roman">)</font><font face="宋体">。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;用兵之術，要在審辨敵人虛實。目能視者，形與色也<font face="Times New Roman">;</font><font face="宋体">耳能聞者，音與聲也</font><font face="Times New Roman">;</font><font face="宋体">然則對方的虛實強弱目不及視，耳不及聞，唯有冥心靜悟，方可察知。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">且</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">張則神馳，引神側凝於一方<font face="Times New Roman">;</font><font face="宋体">耳開則精散，導意偏注於一隅。既此，冥目不視，其神自然歸原</font><font face="Times New Roman">;</font><font face="宋体">塞耳不聽，其意自然返本。師是開導、指迷、傳教、授業者。如目不外視，耳不狂聞，心神專一，勝過用師十倍。再如在晝夜之間，專心致志，精義入神，無有間斷，可以勝過用師萬倍。如</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">瞽</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">者，</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">由</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">聞聲之中善辨其來意<font face="Times New Roman">;</font><font face="宋体">聾者，由視色之中善審其去向，是精氣會集，心神專一之故。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;《莊子<font face="Times New Roman">&middot;</font><font face="宋体">應帝王》中說</font><font face="Times New Roman">:&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">南海之帝為倏，北海之帝為忽，中央之帝為渾沌。倏與忽時相與遇於渾沌之地，渾沌待之甚善。倏與忽謀報渾沌之德曰</font><font face="Times New Roman">:&lsquo;</font><font face="宋体">人皆有七竅，以視聽食息，此獨無有，嘗試鑿之。</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rsquo;</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">日</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">鑿一竅，</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">七日</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">而渾沌死。<font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">耳</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">目</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">所能視聽的，</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">口</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">鼻所能</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">嗅</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">嘗的，身意所能感覺的，僅不過是片面、局部、粗淺的事物之末而已。至於事物精微之奧理，萬化玄妙之本源，唯獨虛明的本來性體，才能了悟。故老君</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">曰</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">:&ldquo;<font face="宋体">常無欲以觀其妙</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">目</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">張則心機馳馳，耳開則精氣散發，以致神志不能專一，性體不能純靜，欲了悟大</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">道</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">者，應閉目返觀內照，塞耳回聽天籟。如此方能心神歸一。<font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">內外相通，心目內觀，真無所有，清淨光明，虛白朗耀，杳杳冥冥，內外無事，昏</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">昏</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">默默，正達無為<font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">。故老君</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">曰</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">:&ldquo;<font face="宋体">五色令人</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">目</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">盲，五音令人耳聾<font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">。又</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">曰</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">:&ldquo;<font face="宋体">塞其兌，閉其門，終身不勤，開其兌，濟其事，終身不救</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;山此可見，人如能將素</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">日</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">所妄貪的世利，絕淨</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">一</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">源，勝如用師傳授十倍。再如能逃出</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">一</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">切塵網，掃除一切塵緣，徹底斬斷六根，</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">方</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">能達到神氣</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">專一</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">，澄心靜慮，萬緣俱消。再如在晝夜中能致虛、守靜，無有間斷，勝過師授萬倍。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;心生於物，死於物，機在目。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;心之所動，欲貪明景，不知不覺，又被物景盜入死地，是<font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">心生於物，死於物</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">也。然則心之有此動機者，是因眼目能視之故，目開心動，心動神馳，追逐物景，迷於世情，紛擾靈根，不能常清常靜。欲修大道者，首先戒慎目不妄視，冥目淨心。故老君</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">曰</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">:&ldquo;<font face="宋体">不見可欲，使心不亂</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">，蓋是此意。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">天</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">之無思，則大</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">恩</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">生，迅</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">雷</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">烈風，</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">莫</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">不</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">蠢</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">然。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;天地無親、無情，不分高低、上下、香臭、軟硬、剛柔、左右、前後、強弱，理窮者必變，物極者必反。更不論榮辱、貴賤、賢愚、尊卑、長幼、親疏、貧富、遠近。體道則存，背理則亡。故</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">曰</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">:&ldquo;<font face="宋体">天之無恩</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;天無私覆，地無私載，雨露不偏施，不論山川、動植、長短、曲直、胎卵、濕化、大小、多少，均獲日月照臨之恩，鹹沾雨露滋潤之惠，故</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">曰</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">:&ldquo;<font face="宋体">則大恩生</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;陰陽消長，雷的震動，風的撓散，雨的澤潤，日的燥暖，萬物因之蠢然而生茂。故曰<font face="Times New Roman">:&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">迅宙烈風，莫不蠢然</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">。又如天以大義主生殺之機，不執斧</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">鉞</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">，不持刑拷，迅雷震威，驚遠懼邇，不論賢人君子，或不肖與小人皆畏懼而自修。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;至樂性</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">餘</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">，至靜性廉。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">餘</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">:<font face="宋体">往來自如，變動不拘，不留不滯，不染不看。廉</font><font face="Times New Roman">:</font><font face="宋体">性體圓明，不染一塵，湛然清澈，廉明清潔。常人以為身得安逸，口得厚味，形得美服，目得好色，耳得好音，富貴壽善者，是為至樂。有道者不然，認為性外的情欲之樂，而非至樂，至樂是無為自然，蕩坦平夷，性體圓明不虧，不妄勞心力，逍遙方外，</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">縱橫自在無拘束，心不貪榮身不辱，閑唱壺中白雪歌，靜調野外陽春曲</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">。不貪不著，自在寬徐。故</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">曰</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">:&ldquo;<font face="宋体">至樂性</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">餘</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&rdquo;<font face="宋体">。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;老君</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">曰</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">:&ldquo;<font face="宋体">致虛極，守靜篤</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">。又</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">曰</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">:&ldquo;<font face="宋体">清靜為天下正</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">。《莊子</font><font face="Times New Roman">&middot;</font><font face="宋体">庚桑楚》中說</font><font face="Times New Roman">:&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">正則靜，靜則明，明則虛，虛則無為而無不為也</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">。</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">水靜則明，平中准，定上下，大匠取法焉。水靜猶明而況精神乎</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">。意即</font><font face="Times New Roman">:&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">能拼眾緣，永除染著</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">。</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">淨掃迷雲無點</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">翳</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">，一輪光滿太虛空<font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">。</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">慧風出自天尊力，掃除心界不遺塵</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">。既是後天的情欲全無，達到虛而至虛，靜而至靜，故謂至靜。使本來的性體光明圓滿，故謂之</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">廉</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">。故老君曰</font><font face="Times New Roman">:&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">滌除玄覽，能無疵乎</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;?</font><font face="宋体">亦是此意。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;天之至私，用之至公。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;老君曰<font face="Times New Roman">:&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">天地所以能長且久者，以其不自生，故能長生。是以聖人，後其身而身先，外其身而身存。以其無私，故能成其私。</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">又雲</font><font face="Times New Roman">:&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">生而不有，為而不恃，功成而不居。夫唯不居，是以不去</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">，</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">火唯不爭，故無尤</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">。天無不覆，地無不載，雨露不偏施，故萬物皆賴雷以動之，風以散之，日以暄之，雨以潤之，而得長之、畜之，是為</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">用之至公</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">。唯獨天地能長生久視者，是為至私。王侯以國事為重，以萬民在心，虛心謙下，自稱孤、寡、不穀者，是用之至公，但江山永固，其位恒久者，是為至私。養生者，心地恬淡虛無，不貪不染，無為自然，積功累德，是為用之至公，因此才能證果成真，位列仙班者，又是至私。本經所說的</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">天之至私，用之至公</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">，實乃治國、處世、修身之妙術也。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;禽之制在氣。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;禽<font face="Times New Roman">:</font><font face="宋体">多以擒縱解，又以飛禽解。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;制<font face="Times New Roman">:</font><font face="宋体">制服。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;老君</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">曰</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">:&ldquo;<font face="宋体">專氣致柔，能如嬰兒乎</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;?</font><font face="宋体">養生之術，全在擒縱與制服氣，使氣與元神合，神不離氣，氣不離神，神氣相守，合凝歸一，長生之道自悟，金丹不煉自成，三寸氣絕，立可</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">喪</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">命。又如飛禽</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">善</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">於操持</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">與</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">能制服氣</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">者</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">，可以任意飛翔，相反，不</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">善</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">於制氣者，反而墜落。治國同然，固國、傾國皆民，善於制服利用臣民者，可以輔國，不善於利用者，可以喪國，常言道<font face="Times New Roman">:</font><font face="宋体">載舟授舟皆水。均在於擒制之術。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;生者死之根，死者生之根。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;根<font face="Times New Roman">:</font><font face="宋体">是因、源之意</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;老君</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">曰</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">:&ldquo;<font face="宋体">吾所以有大</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">忠</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">者，為吾有身。及吾無身，吾有何患<font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">。厚其生，反而喪其生。人有身之後，因貪生惡死，故求厚養其身，縱態奢溢，超常越分，以致禍患來臨，必喪其生。故曰</font><font face="Times New Roman">:&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">生者死之根</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">。如守本分，動止自然，相似不重其生，實能長生。故</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">曰</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">:&ldquo;<font face="宋体">死者生之根</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">。養生之術，亦以此為要訣。故丹經裏所論述的</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">心生性滅，心滅性現</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">，正是此意。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;恩生於</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">害</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">，害生於恩。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;恩害相生，禍福相依，理所當然。孩</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">子</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">蒙父母養育之恩而得成長，如繼續受恩慣養，就成為漂浪之子，一技無成的無用之材，這豈不是由恩中生出害來<font face="Times New Roman">?</font><font face="宋体">如父母對孩子自幼以人倫規範、天理物情的自然之理嚴加教育，使孩子動則成規，止則有矩，為人之楷模。如</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">囊螢</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">，如</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">映雪</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">，如</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&ldquo;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">負薪<font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">，如</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">掛角</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&rdquo;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">，<font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">頭懸樑</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&rdquo;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">，<font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">錐刺股</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">。如此在貧窮苦難之中，不斷深造自己，當時是</font><font face="Times New Roman">:&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">害</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">，將成為輔國棟樑，人中殊甚，這又不是由害中帶來恩惠嗎</font><font face="Times New Roman">?</font><font face="宋体">這就正如孟子所說的</font><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">生於憂患，死於安樂</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">一樣。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;愚人以天地文理聖，我以時物文理哲。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;只知其一，不知其二，知其然，不知其所以然。拘泥於一隅，死守於一方，不能通權達變者，故謂之<font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">愚</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">。日、月、星、辰，風、雲、</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">雷</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">、雨，是天之懸象，故稱<font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">天文</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">。河海山川，金石草木，是地之著</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">形，</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">故稱<font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">地文</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">。天、地、人以及萬事萬物，雖參差不等，其運化之道，是統歸一體，</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">互</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">感形成。如人類的</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">社</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">風民情澆薄奸詐，大道有感，必垂異象，地道亦然，必產奇物。如人類真誠厚樸，天道必清明平靜，地上生物繁榮，五穀豐登。故老君</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">曰</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">:&ldquo;<font face="宋体">師之所處，荊棘生焉。大軍之後，必有凶年</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">。過去還有鄒衍下獄，六月飛霜，齊婦含冤，三年不雨。荊柯刺秦，因精誠感天，故有白虹貫日等這樣的事物之兆。以上正是為天、地、人，萬事、萬物統一運化，相為感應，互為形成的寫證。又常言道</font><font face="Times New Roman">:&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">國正天心順，官清民自安，妻賢夫禍少，子孝父心寬</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">。物與物之間，人與人之際，交接相處，所產生的悲傷憂恐，喜怒哀樂，所形成的吉凶禍福，成敗盛衰，亦是互為影響，相互形成的。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;星辰順序，河海靜默，山嶽穩固，風調雨順，五穀豐登，時和歲</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">稔</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">，這是天地文理之順。星辰失行，四時相錯，旱澇不均，河海不靜，山崩地裂，草木不生，饑年荒歲，這是天地文理之逆。愚人認為天地文理的順逆是天地造就，神聖註定的至理。不可改變的，無法更移的，故只能生恐懷之心，退省自修而已。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;君王體道，國綱大振，巨忠為民效力。民俗淳厚，恭儉退讓，不相傷害，路不拾遺，夜不閉戶，政通人和，這是時物文理之順。君不修德，放蕩淫佚，奢侈不節，仕臣貪權謀利，擅離職守，愚頑作怪，狂徒擾民，賊寇四起，盜劫滋生，這是時物文理之逆。而<font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">我</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">認為時物文理的順、逆是有原因的，並非造定的。《六韜</font><font face="Times New Roman">&middot;</font><font face="宋体">文韜</font><font face="Times New Roman">&middot;</font><font face="宋体">盈虛》中說</font><font face="Times New Roman">:&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">天下熙熙，一盈一虛，一治一亂，所以然者何也</font><font face="Times New Roman">?</font><font face="宋体">其君賢不肖不等乎</font><font face="Times New Roman">?</font><font face="宋体">其天時變化自然</font><font face="Times New Roman">?</font><font face="宋体">太公</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">曰</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">:&lsquo;<font face="宋体">君不肖，則國危而民亂，君賢聖，則國安而民治。禍福在君，不在天時。</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rsquo;&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">既此，沿著事物的形成，追溯事物形成的根源，隨天時應物情，是可以改變的。故老君</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">曰</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">:&ldquo;<font face="宋体">其脆易破，其微易散</font><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">。《周易</font><font face="Times New Roman">&middot;</font><font face="宋体">系辭》中說</font><font face="Times New Roman">:&ldquo;</font><font face="宋体">子殺其父，臣殺其君，</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">非</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">一朝一夕之故，其所由來者漸矣，猶辨之不</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">早</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">辨也<font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><font face="宋体">。意即</font><font face="Times New Roman">:</font><font face="宋体">在</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">事</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">物未形成之前，能辨別清事物的動機，可以制止它的發展和改變事物將來的形成。例如<font face="Times New Roman">:</font><font face="宋体">齊桓公如能辨清易牙烹子奉獻的不良動機，再能傾聽管仲的遺囑，焉能形成身遭困死之禍。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">《黃帝陰符經》<font face="Times New Roman">(</font><font face="宋体">原文</font><font face="Times New Roman">)</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;神仙抱一</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">演</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">道幸第一</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;觀天之道，執天之行，盡央。天有五賊，見之者昌。五賊在心，施行於天。宇宙在乎手，萬化生乎身。天性，人也，人心，機也。立天之道，以定人也。天發殺機，龍蛇起陸。人發殺機，天地反覆。天人合發，萬變定基。性有巧拙，可以伏藏。九竅之邪，在乎三要，可以動靜。火生於木，禍發必克。奸生於國，時動必潰。知之修煉，謂之聖人。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">富</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">國安民演法幸第二</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;天生天殺，道之理也。天地萬物之盜，萬物人之盜，人萬物之盜，三盜既宜，</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">三才既安。故</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">曰</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">:<font face="宋体">食其時，百</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">骸</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">理，動其機，萬化安。人知其神而神，不知不神之所以神也。日月有數，大小有定，聖功生焉，神明出焉。其盜機也，天下莫能見，莫能知，君子得之固躬，小人得之輕命。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;強兵戰勝演術幸第三</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">瞽</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">者善聽，聾者善視，絕利一源，用師十倍，三反晝夜，用師萬倍。心生於物，死於物，機在目。天之無恩，而大恩生，迅雷烈風，莫不蠢然。至樂性餘，至靜性廉。天之至私，用之至公。禽之制在氣。生者死之根，死者生之根。恩生於害，害生於恩。愚人以天地文理聖，我以時物文理哲。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<!--EndFragment-->
	   </div>
	   <div style="text-align:left; color:#88510c; font-size:14px; line-height:20px; width:900px; height:auto; margin:0 auto;">
